---

<PageLayout title={`${title} | Better Lives Building Tribes`} description="You check the news constantly. You scroll through social media looking for updates. You feel a knot in your stomach every time you think about the political climate. You argue with family members, los">
  <Section padding="lg">
    <article class="blog-post">
      <header class="blog-post__header">
        <span class="blog-post__category">{category}</span>
